videos.description: Louisville's Darius Perry comes up with a steal on defense, then throws up a lob to Steven Enoch for the alley-oop slam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Perry, Enoch connect for half-court alley-oop) 2019/12/14

videos.headline: Perry, Enoch connect for half-court alley-oop

videos.description: Louisville's David Johnson drives and uses just one hand to dish a no-look pass to Dwayne Sutton, who swishes home the corner 3.
